kinds of input, and with the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Manchester{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 alliance, so it was continuing from the African stuff.  I was interested in various forms of conflict: what was interesting about the Manchester position was that it asserted that it was in conflict that the
 basic elements of social relations were revealed and restructured, okay?  That conflict produced an insight into normality.  Okay?  And that\rquote 
s where everything floated up, whereas the ordinary everyday was something which filled other things in a suppressed relation.  It was a particular position which}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid1797128 
 they labelled, they called it \lquote situational analysis\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10699196\charrsid10699196 
