\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid2451681\charrsid2451681 Paul:\tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid10699196\charrsid10699196 Yes!
  Well, the last thing that I was hoping you might talk about a bit more, is the story of the Rhodes Livingstone Institute and the group there. Because it is seen, by many people, as very important for the development of anthropology as a whole, isn
