m, writing a public lecture at the moment, on bringing the exotic back in, and saying that it\rquote s not the exotic that\rquote s so important in that sense, in the weird and wonderful type thing, it is the way in wh
ich it challenges conventional positions. That\rquote s why we should be interested in it, not because looks great on television!  (LAUGHS)
